examples.en: They wished her a speedy recovery.
The new network will enable data to be processed more speedily.
He is a speedy worker but not a very careful one, unfortunately.
There was some reason to suppose that all the mortgaged houses would speedily let.
Etching is an imitation of engraving, but more speedily performed.
The figs speedily seize upon the palmyra, enlacing it with their nimble shoots.
